@startuml REQ-0040 OTA Firmware Update
autonumber

entity "Hardware" as Hardware
entity "Cloud" as Cloud

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "OTA Manager" as OTA_Manager
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
end box

header
  **REQ-0040: OTA Firmware Update**
  //Description:// Orchestrate firmware update: download coordination and flash write and verify
  //Acceptance Criteria:// OTA state machine progresses through download/write/verify; CRC passes before reporting success
end header

note over OTA_Manager: OTA_GetProgress()

OTA_Manager --> Comm_Manager: EVENT:COMM_DOWNLOAD_START\nOTA_OnUpdateAvailable() → Comm_DownloadFirmware()
note right of OTA_Manager: OTA_STATE_CHANGE
OTA_Manager --> Hardware: EVENT:HW_FLASH_WRITE\nOTA_OnChunkReceived()
OTA_Manager --> Cloud: EVENT:CLOUD_OTA_RESULT\nOTA_OnDownloadComplete()
OTA_Manager -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus()
note right of OTA_Manager: OTA_VERIFY_CRC

@enduml